Package: gzlmpower
Type: Package
Title: Power Analysis for Generalized Linear Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marcello Gallucci
Maintainer: marcello gallucci <mcfanda@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to compute model-based effect size indices (eta-squared and epsilon-squared) and power parameters for generalized linear models. Conducts power analysis to determine required sample size, minimum effect size, critical alpha, or power based on R-squared or eta-squared.
Imports: pwr, car
